about.projectDescription: SkyHills, the first development in Dubai to partner with Dubai Cares, redefines urban luxury with elegance and purpose. Nestled in a prime location, it offers seamless access to business hubs, top schools, and world-class shopping.

amenities.text: SkyHills Astra offers an array of high-end amenities designed to elevate residents' lifestyles. The building provides 24/7 security and concierge services, ensuring safety and convenience. Thoughtfully designed common areas offer space for leisure and social interaction, while advanced home technology adds to the comfort of daily living. These amenities blend luxury with functionality, creating a balanced and sophisticated residential experience.

content.text: Our installment schemas are devoid of any latent charges or unanticipated costs.
A 4% DLD (Dubai Land Department) fee applies to all real estate transactions in Dubai and must be paid in addition to the property's purchase price.
